{
  "index": 2,
  "title": "Foundations of Blockchain Architecture",
  "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      background-color: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;\n      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vh, 5rem);\n      gap: 2rem;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .slide-header {\n      text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    .slide-header h1 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n\n    .slide-content {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n      gap: 2rem;\n      align-items: start;\n    }\n\n    .concept-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      position: relative;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .concept-card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n\n    .concept-card h2 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-top: 0;\n    }\n\n    .concept-card p {\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n    }\n\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n\n    @keyframes fadeInUp {\n      to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n      }\n    }\n\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-block;\n      font-size: 0.7rem;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n      background: var(--accent-glow);\n      color: var(--text);\n      padding: 2px 8px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">Foundations of Blockchain Architecture</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-content\">\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">Data Integrity</span>\n      <h2>Immutable Ledgers</h2>\n      <p>Cryptographic hashing ensures that once data is written to a block, it cannot be altered without changing every subsequent block. This creates a verifiable, permanent history of transactions.</p>\n      <p><strong>Core:</strong> SHA-256 • Merkle Trees • Chain-of-Trust</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.5s\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">Network Layer</span>\n      <h2>P2P Networking</h2>\n      <p>Distributed nodes maintain the ledger without a central authority. Gossiping protocols ensure state synchronization across the globe with high fault tolerance.</p>\n      <p><strong>Core:</strong> Node Discovery • Gossip Protocols • Decentralization</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.7s\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">Consensus Evolution</span>\n      <h2>The PoW to PoS Shift</h2>\n      <p>Moving from computationally expensive Proof-of-Work (mining) to Proof-of-Stake (validators) drastically reduces the carbon footprint and energy requirements.</p>\n      <p><strong>Impact:</strong> &gt;99% energy reduction • Higher Scalability • Sustainable Growth</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
